  <thing id="cMPSGGCrTc" name="Careful Tactics" description="The investigator is able to analyze a situation and form a set of tactics specifically designed to address it. \n\nIf the investigator can analyze a situation as a fullround action (requiring accurate facts about the situation, though not necessarily direct observation of it) she can select one teamwork feat to grant herself and one ally, +1 ally per 2 investigator levels. The teamwork feat must be one the investigator meets all prerequisites for.\n\nSince plans rarely survive contact with a changing situation, the investigator and her allies retain use of the feat for only 2 rounds per investigator level. \n\nThe investigator may use this ability once per day, +1 once/day per 3 investigator levels." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>Anachronistic Adventurers - The Investigator

Super Genius Games
www.supergeniusgames.com</comment>
    <fieldval field="trkMax" value="1"/>
    <usesource source="MPRGGAnac"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="Secondary"/>
    <tag group="SpecSource" tag="arMHInvest"/>
    <tag group="AbilType" tag="Extra"/>
    <tag group="Usage" tag="Day"/>
    <tag group="User" tag="Tracker"/>
    <eval phase="Level" priority="10000">var hp as number
      hp = 0 + (herofield[tLevel].value / 3)
      hp = round(hp, 0, -1)

      ~ Add to our total charges.
      field[trkMax].value += hp</eval>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cMPSGGCoor" name="Coordinate" description="The investigator is able to analyze the actions of friend and foe alike, and coordinate the efforts of her allies to maximize their potential.\n\nAs a standard action, the investigator may aid another for all allies within 30 feet who are able to see and hear her. \n\nRather than make a melee attack, the investigator makes a special level check (1d20 + investigator level + Wisdom modifier) against a DC of 10 +1 per ally to be aided." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>Anachronistic Adventurers - The Investigator

Super Genius Games
www.supergeniusgames.com</comment>
    <usesource source="MPRGGAnac"/>
    <tag group="AbilType" tag="Extra"/>
