    <tag group="SpecSource" tag="arMHInvest"/>
    <tag group="Usage" tag="Day"/>
    <tag group="AbilType" tag="Extra"/>
    <tag group="ChargeAttr" tag="aINT"/>
    <tag group="User" tag="Tracker"/>
    <tag group="ChargeCalc" tag="AttrUses3"/>
    <tag group="SpecSource" tag="cHelpInv"/>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cMPSGGFlEv" name="Follow the Evidence" description="The investigator can use evidence to form theories about where further evidence can be gained, even when she cannot yet solve a mystery. \n\nOnce per day, the investigator can attempt to determine where further information that helps answer a specific question (such as “Who killed guardsman Maillot Pej?” or “How can the Wraith Queen be killed?” or “How did Professor Abitazione contract Rune Peak Spotted Fever?”) can be found. \n\nThe base chance for this is 70%, +1% per class level, to a maximum of 90%. The GM should make this check in secret. On a successful check, the GM reveals a location likely to lead to more clues or hints that could help answer the question (such as the scene of another crime committed by the same perpetrator, or the ancient crypt where moldering scrolls hold secret lore). \n\nIf not such location exists, or the check is not successful, the investigator cannot come up with any potentially useful location to visit." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>Anachronistic Adventurers - The Investigator

Super Genius Games
www.supergeniusgames.com</comment>
    <usesource source="MPRGGAnac"/>
    <tag group="AbilType" tag="Extra"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="Secondary"/>
    <tag group="SpecSource" tag="arMHInvest"/>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cMPSGGFlTh" name="Follow Through" description="The investigator can use her understanding of leverage and anatomy to leave targets of her combat maneuvers disoriented and vulnerable to melee attacks.\n\nWhenever she makes a successful CMB check to perform a combat maneuver on a foe, she gains a +4 circumstance bonus on the next melee attack roll she makes against the opponent.\n\nThis attack must occur before the end of her next turn, and cannot itself be a CMB check." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>Anachronistic Adventurers - The Investigator

Super Genius Games
www.supergeniusgames.com</comment>
    <usesource source="MPRGGAnac"/>
    <tag group="AbilType" tag="Extra"/>
    <tag group="Helper" tag="Secondary"/>
    <tag group="SpecSource" tag="arMHInvest"/>
    <tag group="SpecSource" tag="arRogInves"/>
    </thing>
  <thing id="cMPSGGFore" name="Forethought" description="The investigator has carefully planned ahead for many eventualities lesser minds would not consider.\n\nOnce per day, she may reroll any one die roll. The decision to reroll must be made before the success or failure of a roll has been revealed, and the investigator must abide by the results of the reroll even if they are worse than the original. \n\nAt 8th level the investigator may reroll twice per day, and at 16th level three times per day." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
    <comment>Anachronistic Adventurers - The Investigator

Super Genius Games
www.supergeniusgames.com</comment>
    <fieldval field="trkMax" value="1"/>
    <usesource source="MPRGGAnac"/>
