  <thing id="cMPSGGStAt" name="Studied Attacks" description="An investigator may use her vast knowledge of creatures, as well as her understanding of her own capabilities, to plan attacks to be most effective against specific foes. \n\nAs a standard action, the investigator may make an appropriate Knowledge check against a creature with a DC of 15 + the creature&apos;s CR. If she succeeds, she may grant herself a circumstance bonus of +1/4 levels to hp damage she deals to the creature with any attack she makes that normally deals hp damage. \n\nIf facing multiple creatures of the same type who have identical defenses, this bonus applies against all of them. \n\nThe bonus lasts for 1 round/ investigator level. The investigator cannot benefit from this ability against more than one foe (or set of identical foes) at a time." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
