  <thing id="fMPSGGGoUn" name="Go Unnoticed" description="{b}Benefit{/b}: During the first round of combat, flat-footed opponents are considered not to have noticed you yet for the purposes of Stealth skill checks, allowing you to make a Stealth check that round to hide from them." compset="Feat" uniqueness="useronce">
