  <thing id="fMPSGGLnRl" name="Landing Roll" description="You have learned the technique of rolling safely away when an enemy trips you.\n\n{b}Benefit{/b}: If you are tripped, you can spend an immediate action to move 5 feet without provoking an attack of opportunity. This does not count as taking a 5-foot step. You fall prone after this movement." compset="Feat" summary="If tripped, move 5 feet as an immediate action" uniqueness="useronce">
