  <thing id="cMPSGGMdEx" name="Medical Expert" description="The medical examiner is a genius in her own field, and applies her vast intellect to solving medical problems in ways other professionals cannot comprehend. \n\nAs a result, she gains a +1 bonus to all Heal checks per 2 class levels. Additionally, each time the medical examiner performs an action that would normally expend a use from a healing kit, there is a percent chance (equal to 50 + the medical examiner&apos;s class level) she manages to preserve enough materials she does not actually lose a use from the kit." compset="ClSpecial">
