  <thing id="cMPSGGBtMd" name="Battlefield Medicine" description="The medical examiner has as much experience patching up and the living as cutting apart the dead, and can do so under terrible conditions. \n\nShe can use the Treat Deadly Wounds function of the Heal skill while expending only a single use from a healer&apos;s kit (instead of the two normally required). She is also able to apply the Treat Deadly Wounds use of the Heal skill as a full-round action (rather than taking the normal hour)." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
