  <thing id="cMPSGGLtBl" name="Lethal Blow" description="The medical examiner&apos;s experience with mortal wounds and knowledge of anatomy give her a keen understanding of where best to land blows in combat.\n\nThe medical examiner gains a 1d6 sneak attack (as the rogue class ability), and a +2 bonus to attack rolls made to confirm critical hits. These bonuses increase to +2d6 sneak attack and +4 to confirm critical hits at 8th level, and +3d6 sneak attack and +6 to confirm critical hits at 16th level." compset="CustomSpec" uniqueness="useronce">
